                <div class="kicker"><span class="kicker"><a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/section/news">NEWS</a></span></div>

                <h1>The Chronicle&#039;s top 10 sports stories of 2017: Marvin Bagley III reclassifies and joins Duke</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/24825c85-6566-4c7d-b34a-3b72f9470913.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Bagley&#x20;has&#x20;been&#x20;a&#x20;force&#x20;for&#x20;Duke&#x20;this&#x20;year.&amp;nbsp&#x3B;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Bagley has been a force for Duke this year.&nbsp;</p>

